        <lb/>M. DC. XLIX. </p>
      <p>
        <pb n="2" facs="https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k57481m/f2.item.r=bpt6k57481m"/>
        <pb n="3" facs="https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k57481m/f3.item.r=bpt6k57481m"/>
        <title type="sub">
